ed!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fsm1665702637040.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fsm1665702637040.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fsm1665702637040.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fsm1665702637040\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\"> Decimal Indicator\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Character to be used for the decimal place indicator for numeric fields in the tree\n    column. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__p_d102923e1_d102924e1_d102925e1\">Valid values:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__li_d41525e1_d41526e1_d41527e1\">Local Default—Use the MS Windows <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Regional\n          and Language Options</span> setting (the default) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__li_d41528e1_d41529e1_d41530e1\">Period—Use the period (<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>) character </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__li_d41531e1_d41532e1_d41533e1\">Comma—Use the comma (<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>) character\n      </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__note_w796ab1b5b5_w797ab1b5_w798ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You can set this property only if you\n      have set the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Sorting</span> property to <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Numeric</span>.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__p_d102926e1_d102927e1_d102928e1\">To set this property dynamically, use the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sce1665702636971.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sce1665702636971.html\" title=\"Uniface list of properties that define the appearance of columns in the Details style of the list view of the tree widget.\">Formats</a> property.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fsm1665702637040__section_zqm_p4h_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d539307e97\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfb1665702636898.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Sorting</a><p>Sort order used for data displayed the selected column at run time.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613109\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613109\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Decimal Indicator Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Decimal Indicator Character to be used for the decimal place indicator for numeric fields in the tree column. Valid values: Local Default—Use the MS Windows Regional and Language Options setting (the default) Period—Use the period ( . ) character Comma—Use the comma ( , ) character Note: You can set this property only if you have set the Sorting property to Numeric . To set this property dynamically, use the Formats property. Applies To utree (Tree) Related Links Sorting Sort order used for data displayed the selected column at run time. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}